FAQ

  • Why did Square Online change to websites?

    We renamed Square Online to websites to better highlight the website-building tools our product offers. All of the same features and capabilities you use today are included to create a full online store — only the name has changed.

  • How do I start my website for free?

    First, start by creating a free Square account. With a Square Free plan, you can immediately start using our website builder  to easily design a professional-looking eCommerce website for your business. Choose between a single ordering page or a multi-page eCommerce website, then customize your order fulfillment methods. Then you’ll be ready to add your products or automatically sync your Square Point of Sale system and start selling. With the Square Free plan, there are no monthly fees or startup costs — just a processing fee when you make a sale.

  • How to create an online store?

    With our website builder, you can create an online store quickly with no coding required. Choose your layout, customize your design, add products, set up payments and shipping, and start selling fast.

    1. Design and customize your site by choosing a layout and personalizing it with your brand’s colors, fonts, and images.

    2. Add your products by listing unlimited items with photos, descriptions, and variations — or by importing them directly from Square POS.

    3. Set up payments and shipping by enabling secure online payments and choosing shipping, pickup, or delivery fulfillment methods.

    4. Connect a custom domain or buy and register a new domain, then publish and launch your site when you’re ready.

    5. Promote your business with built-in SEO tools, marketing, and social integrations, or create a simple shoppable page from your Instagram feed.

    With Square, your in-store and online sales stay synced automatically, making it easy to manage your whole business from one place.

  • Does Square offer resources to help me build my site?

    Yes. You can hire a Square Specialist with the right expertise to help you with eCommerce-specific design, store setup, custom web development, SEO, and more. Whether you’re just starting a business or optimizing for growth, you’ll receive consultation and professional solutions to help drive business results.

  • Can I connect my website to social media?

    Yes. Square offers several built-in integrations to let you connect your Square website with popular social media apps. Reach new customers and drive sales when you integrate with Instagram, Facebook Shops, Google Food Ordering, and Google Product Listings. It’s also easy to get started with a customizable Square Marketing template to send email campaigns, text campaigns, and promotions for Facebook. And with social media integrations, you can post your campaign on Facebook at the same time you send your emails for a complete marketing strategy.

  • Do I get free web hosting when I create a website with Square?

    Yes. Our free web hosting platform provides exceptional speed, performance, and security. With Square, you’ll experience no restriction on bandwidth. Your website includes a free SSL certificate, which ensures that visitors navigate your website over a secure 128-bit encrypted connection. Plus, SSL also helps power eCommerce by enabling customers to check out directly on your domain.
